                <h1>Change Text Object Background Color in Tableau</h1>
                <p>To change the background color of a text object in Tableau, first select the text object in your dashboard. Right-click and choose “Format.” In the Format pane, navigate to the “Shading” section and select the desired background color. This way, you can enhance visibility and aesthetics of your dashboard effectively.</p>
